body:
On and on my body burned, my sheets were wet and cold, the lights were on my eyes were gone, any second I'd lose control, the pounding on my windows was just the pounding in my head, I wonder who was in my room that night who the hell was in my room. There must of been a body there i swear I felt some flesh, it took a little time but I figured they were mine there were fingers coming down my chest, my mouth went through the ceiling and my body fell through the floor, I couldn't find the key coz there was no hole i could see and someone had moved the door. The cops, the priest, the crisis line
No one really had a clue
No one could tell us who was touching me
Or exactly what I should do
My throat was dry, my hopes were high
But nothing really ever got said
But who was in my room last night?
misty looks great with that outfit at page 5
One of the few that I can enjoy without faping
